A simple repository to use confd on docker.

It checks for variables from several resources, such as env, etcd.

To see how it works
1) Have maven installed.
2) Have docker installed and running.
3) Run mvn clean install
4) Run the image -- docker run -d --name nginx rezamda/com.reza.sample-docker-confd:1.0-SNAPSHOT
5) Verify a file is created, and configured in /tmp/myconfig.conf